<h2>Add New Figure</h2>
<form method = "POST" action = "/figures">
<p>Figure name: <input type = "text" name = "figure[name]" id="figure_name"></p>
<p>Pick a title: <%Title.all.each do |title|%>
  <input type = "checkbox" name = "figure[title_ids][]" id="title_<%=title.id%>" value="<%=title.id%>"> <%=title.name%>
<%end%></p>
<p>and/or, Create a brand new title:
  <input type = "text" name = "title[name]" id="new_title"> (ooh, shiny!)</p>

  <br></br>
<p>Assign a landmark: <%Landmark.all.each do |landmark|%>
  <input type = "checkbox" name = "figure[landmark_ids][]" id="landmark_<%=landmark.id%>" value="<%=landmark.id%>"> <%=landmark.name%>
<%end%></p>
<p>and/or, Create a brand new landmark:</p>
<p>Landmark name: <input type = "text" name = "landmark[name]" id="new_landmark">
  Completion Year: <input type = "text" name ="landmark[year_completed]" id="year_completed"> (who's gonna pay for this?)</p>
<p><input type = "submit" value="Create New Figure"></p>
</form>

<br></br>
